item.title: Grove - 125KHz RFID Reader
item.description: This Grove-125KHz RFID Reader is a module used to read uem4100 RFID card information with two output formats: Uart and Wiegand. It has a sensitivity with maximum 7cm sensing distance. There is also the electronic brick version of this module. It can help you with project like internet of thing and access control system. And you should use the module below while using RFID reader: RFID tag combo (125khz)
